social_posts.post_text: Couldn’t decide which era to be, so I went with all of them. Here’s to Eras Tour 🥂✨💕 #arlingtontstheerastour #tstheerastour

Added new vinyls to my filming set up the other day. I’ve been collecting vinyls for a few years now and just find them to be really beautiful. Music in general is an art form that I appreciate, so much so that I’ve dedicated one of my channels to it. An artist’s ability to illustrate their personal experiences and somehow find a way to make those experiences universal and relatable is very special to me. I’m not always the best with words or expressing how I’m feeling so music often fills the gap. Also, music just feels really damn good. What is your favorite album ever? & should I do a vinyl collection tour? 🤔 (full vlog of me getting these vinyls out on the tube @favourreacts) 🎞️
